label.mutableString:
Take-A-Paws was created by Eshani Chauk to help ease the transition of adopted shelter dogs to their new homes through music therapy. This app can also be used to calm your dog if he/she becomes nervous or overexcited. Take-A-Paws allows you to add your favorite songs from the app's songs to the playlist and play them repeatedly for up to 24 hours. All songs are played and recorded by Eshani Chauk.
** Disclaimer: Take-A-Paws is not intended to solve problems such as separation anxiety or fear of certain sounds/objects. It is only meant to be a helpful aide to lower stress levels in your dog. **
